    "( 1) and ( 2), an interaction-based graph G is generated using a sequence of online learning activities.",
    "An interaction-based graph can be expressed asG(T) = {V(T), E(T)}, (5)V(T) = {i: ∃v i (t) ∈, t ∈ T },(6)E(T) = {(i, j): ∃e i, j (t) ∈, t ∈ T }, (7) = {x(t 1), x(t 2),...}, 0 ≤ t 1 ≤ t 2 ≤ • • •, (8)where x(t i) denotes an interaction event in the sequence of online learning activities.",
